777
01:03:53,163 --> 01:03:59,163
微睡に余白の答え
...and the answer in the margins of my slumber.

778
01:03:59,163 --> 01:04:06,163
白いページに色が咲いていく
On the white page, colors begin to bloom...

779
01:04:06,163 --> 01:04:12,663
息づいた景色を描き出す
...painting a scenery brought to life.

780
01:04:12,663 --> 01:04:15,663
All the colors I held back

781
01:04:15,663 --> 01:04:19,163
Start to gather in the hush

782
01:04:19,163 --> 01:04:22,663
"It's all right," the first light tells me

783
01:04:22,663 --> 01:04:25,963
Sending warmth into my heart

784
01:04:25,963 --> 01:04:28,663
願いも希望も
Neither my wishes nor my hopes...

785
01:04:28,663 --> 01:04:31,963
隠さなくていいんだよ
...do you need to hide anymore.

786
01:04:31,963 --> 01:04:35,163
ほら、ありのままの
Look, just as you are...

787
01:04:35,163 --> 01:04:38,663
私を描く
...I will draw myself.

788
01:05:07,671 --> 01:05:10,271
At last, hold my true colors

789
01:05:10,271 --> 01:05:14,071
ほどけた輪郭も
Even the unraveled outlines,

790
01:05:14,071 --> 01:05:17,371
そっと、ずっと、重なって
are gently, forever overlapping,

791
01:05:17,371 --> 01:05:20,371
私の形になる
becoming my shape.

792
01:05:20,671 --> 01:05:23,371
静かな始まりに
In a quiet beginning,

793
01:05:23,671 --> 01:05:30,871
目覚めた色を抱いて
embracing the awakened colors.

794
01:05:33,071 --> 01:05:36,071
I'm drawing out my true colors

795
01:05:36,371 --> 01:05:39,871
滲んだ輪郭も
Even the blurred outlines,

796
01:05:39,871 --> 01:05:42,871
淡く、脆く、煌めいて
faintly, fragrantly shimmering,

797
01:05:42,871 --> 01:05:45,871
形になってゆくの
taking shape.

798
01:05:46,071 --> 01:05:48,871
夜明けの面影を
Gathering the traces of dawn,

799
01:05:49,071 --> 01:05:54,871
集めた色で描く
I draw with the colors gathered.

800
01:05:55,071 --> 01:05:58,671
draw it slow, draw it true

801
01:05:58,871 --> 01:06:05,371
Ah...

802
01:06:05,871 --> 01:06:11,871
La la la...

803
01:06:20,371 --> 01:06:24,371
draw it slow, draw it true

804
01:06:27,871 --> 01:06:32,871
夢のぬくもりと
Dream's warmth and

805
01:06:33,371 --> 01:06:39,871
指先に絵の具の匂い
the scent of paint on my fingertips.

806
01:06:40,671 --> 01:06:45,871
ありふれた朝の先には
Beyond the ordinary morning,

807
01:06:46,371 --> 01:06:52,871
まだ知らない色が溢れてる
colors I don't know yet are overflowing.

808
01:07:14,971 --> 01:07:17,371
Raoooo!

809
01:07:17,871 --> 01:07:20,371
Ciao everyone! I'm still here.

810
01:07:20,671 --> 01:07:24,071
I just wanted to say thank you so, so much...

811
01:07:24,071 --> 01:07:27,871
...for watching my first ever 3D birthday live!

812
01:07:28,371 --> 01:07:30,871
I had so much fun, and I hope you...

813
01:07:30,871 --> 01:07:33,371
...I hope you had so much fun, too!

814
01:07:33,371 --> 01:07:36,871
I worked really, really hard, and I'm so happy right now.

815
01:07:36,871 --> 01:07:39,871
So thank you Chatini! Thank you everyone for watching!

816
01:07:39,871 --> 01:07:42,871
見てくれてありがとうございました！
Thank you so much for watching!

817
01:07:42,871 --> 01:07:46,371
So, I have to go now. Bye-bye!

818
01:07:46,371 --> 01:07:48,871
And remember, big cat means...

819
01:07:48,871 --> 01:07:50,871
...big trouble!

820
01:07:50,871 --> 01:07:53,371
Raoooo!

821
01:07:55,871 --> 01:07:57,371
Raoooo!

822
01:07:57,371 --> 01:08:01,071
Ciao everyone! I have one last message for you all.

823
01:08:01,371 --> 01:08:05,371
Be sure to check out the MV premiere right after this!

824
01:08:05,371 --> 01:08:08,371
And also, my new original song will be releasing...

825
01:08:08,371 --> 01:08:11,371
...on all streaming platforms on May 11th midnight...

826
01:08:11,371 --> 01:08:13,371
...in your local timezone.

827
01:08:13,371 --> 01:08:15,371
So don't miss it out, okay?

828
01:08:15,371 --> 01:08:17,071
Also, go check out my merch!

829
01:08:17,071 --> 01:08:18,671
Bye bye-bye!

830
01:08:18,671 --> 01:08:20,871
Raoooo!

831
01:08:20,871 --> 01:08:22,871
Bye-bye!

